channel.title: Fastive Lines - Tropical Original *Fixed*
channel.description:
Hello everybody! As you all know that my last post was closed. I needed to make a new one and didn't want to confuse everybody. (Heads up i wanted the post closed if you all were wondering)
Anyways... Again... Im making a new album here within the next month. You can see more information from the link below!
Topic: https://disco.auxy.co/t/new-album-coming-next-month/6827
Well folks, here is my new song! This is fixed up a bit from the last time i posted it. There was certain things wrong with the song but its all fixed!
Here it is: [Fastive Lines - Tropical Original](https://soundcloud.com/tropical_madman/fastive-lines-tropical-1)
You all have a wonderful day!
